From: "Isaac J. Manjarres" <isaacmanjarres@google.com>
Date: Sat, 15 Nov 2025 00:27:09 +0000
Subject: ANDROID: rust: file: Add a helper for reading file size from an inode

This will be used in a subsequent patch by the Rust ashmem driver's
memfd compatibility logic to implement ASHMEM_GET_SIZE for memfds.

Bug: 370906207
Bug: 415769373
Bug: 456158356
Change-Id: I7cfd88b4f1c2c2b5dc5f8ef1a77a5286659ac440
Signed-off-by: Isaac J. Manjarres <isaacmanjarres@google.com>
---
 rust/helpers/fs.c | 5 +++++
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+)

diff --git a/rust/helpers/fs.c b/rust/helpers/fs.c
--- a/rust/helpers/fs.c
+++ b/rust/helpers/fs.c
@@ -10,3 +10,8 @@ struct file *rust_helper_get_file(struct file *f)
 {
 	return get_file(f);
 }
+
+loff_t rust_helper_i_size_read(const struct inode *inode)
+{
+	return i_size_read(inode);
+}
